channel.title: Help, Can't log on with the Ip I made on No-Ip
channel.description:
Downloaded D D S P 3 C V5 in october, next day, couldn't log on my server. Here are some pics of what I have... Correctly
Port Forwarding: [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/2j1wizq.jpg[/img]
Environment Variables: [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/2rd93m9.jpg[/img]
I have I Pk N Edge V2. Whenever I hit runserver.bat, It says this... [code]WorldObjects.cfg: File not found Starting server on 0.0.0.0:43594[/code]
I can log on with 0.0.0.0, but not my no-ip's Ip, people try to log on my server with ip 0.0.0.0, but they can't get on, how come only I can? Please help >.<. Can you tell me how I can log on with my No-Ip? Thanks.
!~!>~C~<!~!

item.title: Help, Can't log on with the Ip I made on No-Ip
item.dc:creator: @i_pk_120 i pk 120
item.description:
@i_pk_120 wrote:

Get a new source probably, because theres an error in that source: WordObjects.cfg: File not found.
And for your IP problem, 0.0.0.0 or 127.0.0.1 is your localhost so you can log on even if you dont have internet, and I suggest you portforward with utorrent. Theres a GREAT guide stickied. It really helped me and I am hosting my server on utorrent.
